dc_description_s: This data represents roads for Lincoln County, Wisconsin in 2024.[This data set consists of digital map files containing road centerline information obtained predominantly by conducting field work using GPS technology and Orthophotography. Features contained in the data set include all road centerlines countywide and associated attributes.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.co.lincoln.wi.us/webapps/gisportal/data.html
